generalDescription: This test case describes when a patient is administered two doses of the Janssen Covid-19 vaccine and one dose of the Pfizer Covid-19 as a third dose (second booster) at an interval of 4 months, that the dose is valid.  Another dose should be forecast.
reasonForChange: v4.27  Updated test case to a fixed date test case to retain previous booster recommendations before the updated Covid-19 Interim Clinical Guidance (09/02/2022).
